data.description: Welcome to your NextHome in Portsmouth, VA! This recently renovated brick beauty boasts four bedrooms and two bathrooms, offering ample space for comfortable living. Step inside to discover an open inviting floor plan.The kitchen has stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. Outside, a private backyard oasis awaits, perfect for relaxing or hosting summer barbecues. Located near military bases, interstates, casino, and much more! Home was renovated in 2020, but does need some TLC. Seller is offering a $10,000 home improvement allowance (flooring, paint, landscaping, etc.) to be used at the buyer's discretion AND 3% towards the buyer's closing costs! Don't miss your chance to turn this house into a home—schedule a showing today!
